result.name: Showa Shokudo

reviews.text: Sushimi and deep fried choices are very nice....串燒needs improvement...

Nice Japanese decorated Izakaya restaurant with varieties of great authentic Japanese sushi, sashimi situated  in Causeway Bay with extended operating hours till 2:00 am from Monday to Saturday. Many collection of Sake labels sticked on the ceiling of the restaurant and Elegant food presentation together with waiters’ explanation on tasting sequence of every piece of sushi make sure you know about the food and sake matching . Don’t forget to try nice sake together with food. There are many nice Generation 14th Sake matching with sashimi, sushi, BBQ  sticks. Priority booking is essential for such arrangement.

Food should be ordered slowly over several courses rather than all at once, tofu sorbet dessert must be tried for a completely enjoyable meal. Master chef Cheung gives me surprising fresh cuisine on my every visits. 

This izakaya restaurant offer a choice of both seating by the bar or tables in VIP room. I highly recommend this restaurant is good for gathering and celebration dinners with friends and clients.

Very cute Japanese restaurant that nicely decorated as old time. Super friendly staffs with a wide variety of Japanese food and all are yummy 
They also have their own brand of sake that come with their chefs portrait as logo sticker, pretty cute.

Nicely decorated Japanese restaurant, and food is great too.  
The whole restaurant is themed with old time of Japan, and with all the billboard and design.  Food is generally OK, but not surprising.  Staffs are friendly and help to explain the food.  As the shop is not big, and tables are limited
Friendly services and good Japanese food

result.adr_address: 香港灣仔謝斐道391號
result.name: 昭和食堂

reviews.text: 食物不錯，可是詢問落單情況時師傅們只對吧枱食客談天說地而被忽略，感覺不爽
想不到在灣仔的暗巷內有氣氛這麼棒的餐廳，食物的選擇雖然不是超多，但吃得出誠意

天后前「酒樂亭」老闆最近夥拍唐文龍和劉永健，在灣仔開設居酒屋「昭和食堂」。
門口髹上巨型昭和年代食堂境況的油畫，十分矚目！
並將多年來在日本夜冷店搜羅的舊廣告牌、郵局門牌、和紙燈籠、懷舊玩具，都掛滿店中。
而且地點十分方便，港鐵銅鑼灣站 C 出口, 步行約4分鐘便可到達。

門前一幅以昭和時期的街道為背景,而且店內使用日本產白米

餐牌都十分有特色、富心思。

菜式選擇豐富，自選人前可以有手卷、刺身、吉列豬扒、天婦羅、魚柳等等，而再配飽肚飯餐，性價比高。
如果都無所選擇，其實還有不少定食可供選擇。

價錢不算貴，而食材較一般居酒屋更講究。

店內裝潢營造日式風格，充滿懷舊氣氛，除了掛滿了和紙燈籠、郵局門牌、懷舊玩具，還貼滿昔日的鐵皮廣告作裝飾，更不斷播放着日語金曲，相當有氣氛。

主打時令刺身，依據當日有甚麼特色貨，詳列於黑板上。
午市有套餐，包含了主菜魚生、前菜及味潧湯。魚生新鮮，而且環境舒服:like:
環境舒適， 懷舊設計， 食品新鮮 有特色， 置身於日本一樣！
日式白飯，淋淋的，魚生麻麻，不會再光顧
